1
00:00:41,251 --> 00:00:42,952
{\an1}I had nothing at all.

2
00:00:47,724 --> 00:00:50,760
{\an1}It's still not enough yet!

3
00:00:52,396 --> 00:00:57,835
{\an1}This still... isn't...
who I am!

4
00:01:02,206 --> 00:01:06,111
{\an1}And that is why I've
kept on adding to myself.

5
00:01:08,346 --> 00:01:11,082
{\an1}So what I want right now
is not your lecture,

6
00:01:11,116 --> 00:01:14,152
but instead your
abilities and intel.

7
00:01:14,686 --> 00:01:17,055
{\an1}Not only are you a Leaf
Shinobi, you're of the

8
00:01:17,088 --> 00:01:19,225
{\an1}famed Uchiha bloodline.

9
00:01:19,258 --> 00:01:22,461
{\an1}You possess Sharingan that
have awakened the Mangekyo.

10
00:01:22,495 --> 00:01:25,598
{\an1}You also bore many secrets
and stopped a war...

11
00:01:25,631 --> 00:01:28,968
{\an1}And you had many jutsu
and a lot of power.

12
00:01:29,302 --> 00:01:32,104
{\an1}Itachi, you possessed
many things that

13
00:01:32,138 --> 00:01:34,608
{\an1}made you who you are.

14
00:01:34,641 --> 00:01:38,946
{\an1}There is no finer foil to my
Reanimation Jutsu than you.

15
00:01:40,113 --> 00:01:42,749
And my pawns are
part of my power.

16
00:01:43,884 --> 00:01:45,018
{\an1}You exaggerate...

17
00:01:45,986 --> 00:01:47,854
{\an1}The reality is, I failed.

18
00:01:48,255 --> 00:01:49,524
{\an1}[harrumphing chuckle]

19
00:01:49,856 --> 00:01:51,725
No... earlier.

20
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:54,362
{\an1}Even though I may have
mocked the Uchiha name in

21
00:01:54,395 --> 00:01:56,264
{\an1}front of you, I have
to admit that I'm

22
00:01:56,297 --> 00:01:58,666
{\an1}actually still quite
envious of it.

23
00:01:59,601 --> 00:02:02,003
{\an1}The Uchiha name merely
indicates a bloodline and

24
00:02:02,036 --> 00:02:03,137
clan membership.

25
00:02:03,871 --> 00:02:06,408
{\an1}It's meaningless for
you to claim it.

26
00:02:16,018 --> 00:02:18,387
{\an1}<i>From the very beginning,</i>
<i>I was nobody...</i>

27
00:02:22,225 --> 00:02:23,693
<i>I had nothing.</i>

28
00:02:26,229 --> 00:02:27,998
{\an1}I bet he's from that city...

29
00:02:28,031 --> 00:02:29,866
{\an1}Where that recent
battle was just fought.

30
00:02:31,167 --> 00:02:32,802
{\an1}Where are your parents?

31
00:02:35,038 --> 00:02:38,074
{\an1}Don't worry. Just relax. I
can help. I'm able to do a

32
00:02:38,108 --> 00:02:39,776
{\an1}little Medical Ninjutsu.

33
00:02:43,581 --> 00:02:46,217
{\an1}Wait, how about...
Kabuto, as in helmet?

34
00:02:46,484 --> 00:02:47,485
So simple.

35
00:02:47,518 --> 00:02:48,352
That was fast.

36
00:02:48,386 --> 00:02:49,621
It's just what
he's wearing!

37
00:02:49,655 --> 00:02:52,056
{\an1}It's best not to overthink
things sometimes.

38
00:02:52,691 --> 00:02:56,295
{\an1}Until I was given a name and
a place to call home....

39
00:02:57,162 --> 00:02:59,865
{\an1}You think that claiming
a name is meaningless?

40
00:03:00,165 --> 00:03:01,400
It's not.

41
00:03:01,734 --> 00:03:03,636
It does hold
meaning for me!

42
00:03:05,070 --> 00:03:07,674
{\an1}Are you sure it would
be bad to kill him?

43
00:03:07,707 --> 00:03:09,742
{\an1}As it is, we're stuck
playing catch-up!

44
00:03:09,776 --> 00:03:12,578
{\an1}I already told you no! He
controls the battlefield

45
00:03:12,612 --> 00:03:14,414
{\an1}right now. Be patient.

46
00:03:14,947 --> 00:03:16,983
Is the Izanami
still not ready?!

47
00:03:17,016 --> 00:03:18,418
{\an1}He's about to attack!

48
00:03:23,189 --> 00:03:26,125
{\an1}Don't worry, Sasuke. I'm on
it. It's just going to take

49
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,661
{\an1}a little more time.

50
00:03:27,927 --> 00:03:31,031
{\an1}Lord Orochimaru said
this to me once.

51
00:03:31,065 --> 00:03:33,667
{\an1}Sakon! Demon Twin Jutsu!

52
00:03:35,903 --> 00:03:38,305
{\an1}Jirobo! Earth Style:
Terra Shield!

53
00:03:46,681 --> 00:03:49,785
{\an1}If you want to know who and
what you are, all you need

