66
00:04:25,956 --> 00:04:27,891
Inferno Style!
Flame Control!

67
00:04:37,301 --> 00:04:38,804
{\an1}They ran to the back, huh?

68
00:04:40,773 --> 00:04:42,508
{\an1}Too bad it's no use!

69
00:04:43,141 --> 00:04:46,478
{\an1}Tayuya! Demon Flute:
Chains of Fantasia!

70
00:04:50,416 --> 00:04:51,818
{\an1}Are you okay, Sasuke!

71
00:04:57,156 --> 00:04:58,290
Genjutsu, huh?

72
00:04:59,291 --> 00:05:01,528
{\an1}Even your precious
Susano'o can't block

73
00:05:01,561 --> 00:05:03,396
{\an1}out sound, can it?

74
00:05:03,763 --> 00:05:04,998
