75
00:05:05,532 --> 00:05:09,002
{\an1}Now that I've immobilized
you, all that's left is...

76
00:05:11,538 --> 00:05:14,642
{\an1}To absorb you using
Lord Orochimaru!

77
00:07:00,855 --> 00:07:01,488
[gasp]

78
00:07:05,726 --> 00:07:09,263
{\an1}Well, Sasuke? How about it?
Do you remember this?

79
00:07:09,297 --> 00:07:11,599
{\an1}You recognize this
current form of mine?

80
00:07:12,099 --> 00:07:12,600
That's--

81
00:07:15,536 --> 00:07:18,306
{\an1}Thanks to you,. I was
finally able to take Lord

82
