killed him!

84
00:07:26,214 --> 00:07:26,915
That's right!

85
00:07:27,984 --> 00:07:30,887
{\an1}I've achieved it at last!
This is my true form!

86
00:07:31,119 --> 00:07:33,622
{\an1}Remember, I said that all
the laws and principles of

87
00:07:33,656 --> 00:07:35,424
Nature, which
Lord Orochimaru

88
00:07:35,457 --> 00:07:39,395
{\an1}researched and compiled for
so long, are now stored and

89
00:07:39,429 --> 00:07:41,364
{\an1}being used inside of me.

90
00:07:41,397 --> 00:07:43,232
{\an1}The only thing that
was missing...

91
00:07:43,266 --> 00:07:46,003
...was Lord
Orochimaru himself!

92
00:07:46,336 --> 00:07:47,972
But now, as you
see, I possess

93
00:07:48,005 --> 00:07:49,807
{\an1}him inside of me, too!

94
00:07:50,473 --> 00:07:53,510
{\an1}I really can't thank
you enough, Sasuke!

95
00:07:54,612 --> 00:07:57,314
{\an1}Kabuto... You are
not Orochimaru.

96
00:07:58,415 --> 00:08:00,684
{\an1}It's fine to imitate
someone you respect...

97
00:08:00,718 --> 00:08:04,254
{\an1}But don't remake yourself
into him to that extent.

98
00:08:07,926 --> 00:08:10,395
{\an1}You do realize a majority
of people start out by

99
00:08:10,428 --> 00:08:12,998
{\an1}mimicking another person
they admire, don't you?

100
00:08:13,865 --> 00:08:17,202
{\an1}Just like the way
Sasuke emulated you.

101
00:08:19,437 --> 00:08:20,605
[gulp]

102
00:08:39,225 --> 00:08:41,461
{\an1}Wow, Itachi! You nailed
every target, even the one

103
00:08:41,495 --> 00:08:43,764
{\an1}in the blind spot
behind the rock!

104
00:08:43,797 --> 00:08:45,999
All right, now
it's my turn!

105
00:08:47,167 --> 00:08:48,903
No, Sasuke. It's
time to go.

106
00:08:48,936 --> 00:08:49,670
[grunt]

107
00:08:50,771 --> 00:08:52,840
{\an1}What happened to the new
shuriken jutsu you promised

108
00:08:52,874 --> 00:08:54,241
{\an1}to teach me, huh?

109
00:08:54,274 --> 00:08:55,543
