talking about.

176
00:14:11,846 --> 00:14:14,615
{\an1}Anyway, that's enough of
your word games.

177
00:14:14,648 --> 00:14:16,550
{\an1}I will have everything
that I want!

178
00:14:16,951 --> 00:14:18,387
{\an1}I'm the strongest of all!

179
00:14:18,886 --> 00:14:21,089
{\an1}That is a simple fact!

180
00:14:22,457 --> 00:14:25,327
{\an1}He who forgives himself and
acknowledges his true self...

181
00:14:26,594 --> 00:14:28,163
[growl roar]

182
00:14:28,363 --> 00:14:30,098
