{\an1}<i>How? I cut off my sight...</i>

189
00:15:10,475 --> 00:15:12,811
{\an1}I should be invulnerable
to genjutsu.

190
00:15:13,244 --> 00:15:14,746
{\an1}But this is clearly...

191
