[screaming]

192
00:15:35,801 --> 00:15:37,270
{\an1}What did you do to me?!

193
00:15:38,438 --> 00:15:40,507
I have you in
my Visual Jutsu.

194
00:15:41,041 --> 00:15:41,807
Huh?

195
00:15:43,176 --> 00:15:44,344
Impossible!

196
