198
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:54,821
Well, it doesn't
matter anyway.

199
00:15:54,855 --> 00:15:57,458
Because no one
can stop me now!

200
00:15:58,259 --> 00:16:00,128
{\an1}I am all-powerful!

201
00:16:22,084 --> 00:16:26,356
{\an1}As I told you... I hold your
fate in my hands right now!

202
00:16:26,556 --> 00:16:28,857
Itachi Uchiha!

203
00:16:38,402 --> 00:16:39,802
{\an1}If this is a genjutsu...

204
00:16:43,607 --> 00:16:44,575
Release!

205
00:16:51,081 --> 00:16:51,616
Huh?

206
00:16:53,384 --> 00:16:54,318
[growling]

207
