227
00:18:33,224 --> 00:18:34,692
{\an1}Don't mess with me!

228
00:18:44,736 --> 00:18:46,438
{\an1}He cannot escape this loop.

229
00:18:46,971 --> 00:18:49,408
{\an1}He'll remain stuck
inside this samsara.

230
00:18:50,908 --> 00:18:53,612
{\an1}So this is the other Uchiha
Forbidden Jutsu, the

231
00:18:53,645 --> 00:18:55,080
{\an1}companion to Izanagi.

